name: Gungan General
Lore: 'Man Gungans spend years studying the art of war in the depths of Otoh Gunga. Only at the Battle of Naboo were these Gungans able to exercise that knowledge. Leader.',
Text: 'Deploys -1 to Naboo. Your Gungans at same site are firfeit +2. While in a battle, if you just drew a Gungan for battle destiny you may take that card into hand.',
